      "content": "A recent preprint on bioRxiv (doi: 10.1101/2023.03.14.532669) suggests novel therapeutic designs that couple miRNA mimics with epigenetic modulators for precise control of immune cell differentiation. Early data show a significant decrease in NF-κB activation markers in preclinical arthritis models.",
